Package dog.giraffe.image

Class FileImageWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • dog.giraffe.image.FileImageWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImageWriter, Log, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public class FileImageWriter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ImageWriter
    An ImageWriter that writes an image line by line to the disk directly. Instances will only buffer line data for lines actively written to by some thread.
